net.rptools.maptool.model.MacroButtonPro.label: dnd5e_RollExpression_getRoll
net.rptools.maptool.model.MacroButtonPro.toolTip: Returns the effective roll created by the DiceRoller on the RollExpression. This is the raw roll without any bonus or child expressions added. Depending on the ExpressionType, this may either be the representative roll (as in the cases of advantage or disadvantage) or may simply be the most recent roll in the case of multipl totalRolls.
